description: Allows the specified user to access the FinSpace web application and API.

parameters.name: userId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the user that you want to activate.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A token that ensures idempotency. This token expires in 10 minutes. This field is autopopulated if not provided.
